(41, 11, 24, 62, 3, 22, 22, 'when ye pray, believe that ye receive them', 'Connection of Prayer and Belief', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of belief in prayer and obedience to God''s commandments. Mark 11:24 highlights believing in what is desired in prayer, while 1 John 3:22 connects receiving answers to keeping commandments and pleasing God.', 'theme', 1.0, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
